    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Oracle Elemental Mystery Power</strong><br/><br/><p>Air and fire shroud you from your enemies' vision and superheat your strikes in combat. You can surround yourself with heated air as a swift action, gaining concealment (as per the blur spell). At 7th level while you are using this ability, your melee attacks each deal an additional 2 points of fire damage. You can use this ability for 1 minute per oracle level per day; this duration does not need to be consecutive, but it must be spent in 1-minute increments. You must be at least 3rd level to select this revelation.</p>",
